text: Suzanne M. Kosmas (born February 25, 1944) is an American politician and real estate broker. She was the U.S. Representative for for one term from 2009 until 2011. She is a member of the Democratic Party. She was a member of the Florida House of Representatives between 1996 until 2004. ==References== Category:1944 births Category:Living people Category:Real estate developers Category:United States representatives from Florida Category:Politicians from Washington, D.C.
